msgstr "當敵人伸手去拿 %{name} 時，它神祕地消失了。"

msgid "Necromancy!"
msgstr "亡靈巫術！"

msgid ""
"Practicing the dark arts of necromancy, you are able to raise %{count} of "
"the enemy's dead to return under your service as %{monster}."
msgstr ""
"藉由施展亡靈巫術的黑暗力量，你復活了 %{count} 具敵方屍體，化為 %{monster} 為"
"你效力。"

