"value"
msgstr ""
"預設\n"
"數值"

msgid "Set %{skill} Skill:"
msgstr "設定 %{skill} 技能："

msgid "Set %{skill} base value. Right-click to reset all skills to default."
msgstr "設定 %{skill} 基礎值。右鍵按一下可將所有技能重置為預設。"

msgid "View %{skill} Info"
msgstr "檢視 %{skill} 資訊"

