msgid "The three Anduran artifacts magically combine into one."
msgstr "三件 Anduran 神器神奇地合而為一。"

msgid "View Spells"
msgstr "檢視法術"

msgid "View %{name} Info"
msgstr "檢視 %{name} 資訊"

